         <abstract id="aspace_9009b227bbfb4a74b2ad98fa494ac8d6">The collection contains photographs, slides, and pictures of Davenport College and Pierson College at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views, views of the masters" houses, dining halls, and courtyards, as well as photographs documenting construction.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_3efdb374c9a1ba60af4e2c8982eac62f">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
